ygData.messageBody:
There is one vendor in the Freeport clerics guilds who sells all heal,
endure, resurrect type of spells. If you have ever bought heal spells there
before then you have talked to that vendor
Bree Wyndsdale
46th Cleric Of Fennin Ro
